               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Name of St. Mary; names of the donors and of the scribe (not always); the word sälam; other words: zä-ʾaqǝräbku (fol. 78vb l.38), nägäśt (fol. 140rc l.11), bä-sǝbḥatä (fol. 157rb l.9), bä-qal (fol. 194va l.2); incipits of the text and its sections (a few lines are rubricated, alternating with black lines, at the beginning of each monthly reading: fols. 3r, 40r, 70r, 103r, 142r, 184v); elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
