eight: 115%;"><br /> </span></span></span></p><foreign xml:lang="en"><p>Fol. 211vc l.12: Believing in prayer of our Lady Mary I wrote it and completed it on the 3rd of N&#228;&#7717;ase with hard labours, do not forget me during the time in which (the book) is read. For ever and ever. And the writing of this book &lt;&#8230;&gt;; and his kinsmen G&#228;br&#228; Kr&#601;stos and Z&#228;r&#704;a Yo&#7717;ann&#601;s, and the administrator of the church Y&#228;man&#228; Kr&#601;stos, son of &#7716;ayl&#228; &#704;Iy&#228;sus, do not forget them (to recite) Pater Noster.</p></foreign>
